title: MomentJSExample

This shows is a brief example showing the use of moment.js in TiddlyWiki5.

A small javascript macro called `datemodified` allows us to insert the date
the document was modified at any point in any tiddler, see the site subtitle
for an example using the calendar function.

This:

```
<<datemodified>>
<<datemodified calendar>>
<<datemodified YYYY>>
```

Shows up like this:

<<datemodified>>

<<datemodified calendar>>

<<datemodified YYYY>>

